{
  "texts": [
    "However, training large language models poses considerable challenges, as it necessitates an abundance of text data and extremely powerful computational resources.",
    "This makes it difficult for individual users and researchers to train such models from scratch.",
    "Consequently, the industry typically adopts the practice of fine-tuning pretrained large models, which has yielded impressive results in numerous practical application scenarios.",
    "Merging large language models with TAD could result in novel advancements and breakthroughs.",
    "TAD can capitalize on the language understanding competencies of large language models to gain a deeper comprehension and interpretation of action content in videos."
  ]
}